 # Changelog
 
+## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S4-P04-T055 (A2 production gate; NOT_DEPLOYED)
+
+- Fifty-fifth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S4-P04), closing S4-P04. An A2 production gate that promotes an A2 functional zone to continuous production ONLY on real 30-day health evidence and keeps the rest disabled or low-frequency. release_mode NOT_DEPLOYED; a gate/decision task, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/a2_production_gate.py scores all 18 A2 zones from the T053 pilot and the T054 expansion, measures each zone's observed health days, and decides promote (health days >= 30) / low_frequency / disabled. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S4-P04-T055/: a2_promotion_ledger.json (promotion ledger + cost/quality evidence + rollback), known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND; verifier hardened to deep per-entry re-derivation). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S4-P04-T055/test-results/gate_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): 0 zones are promoted just to hit a count target since promotion requires health evidence, never value or coverage; every promoted source would carry >= 30-day health, which holds since 0 are promoted because no A2 zone has 30-day health yet (their portals are JS/TLS-blocked and fetch is deferred), giving the honest outcome of 3 zones held low_frequency (1-day recon) and 15 disabled (0-day); and the gate is non-vacuous, since a control proves it promotes a source with 35-day health and does NOT promote a high-value source with only 5-day health, run through the same decide() path. Each held zone carries a days_to_promotion reason; deliverables include the ledger, cost/quality evidence, and a rollback path; decisions are reversible (NOT_DEPLOYED, feature flag, no production rewrite). Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
+
 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S4-P04-T054 (expand A2 registry by marginal value; SHADOW)
 
 - Fifty-fourth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S4-P04). Expands the A2 registry beyond the T053 first-10 pilot by MARGINAL value, adding only zones that actually provide first-line local-action signals. release_mode SHADOW; a selection/expansion task, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/a2_registry.py builds on the T053 model: baseline_from_t053 (the existing A2 verified-useful-signal rate), evaluate (a candidate's first-line signals beyond the A0/A1 baseline plus its official identity), useful_signal_rate, and expand (admit only verified-useful zones; the new cohort rate must be at or above the baseline). Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S4-P04-T054/: a2_expansion.json (cohorts + marginal value report + health), known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S4-P04-T054/test-results/expansion_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): the existing A2 baseline (the T053 pilot) has a verified-useful-signal rate of 1.0; the expansion admits 8 more high-value functional zones (Nansha, Zhoushan, Xihai'an, Hefei hi-tech, East-Lake hi-tech, Binhai, Jiangbei, Chengdu hi-tech), each official with at least one first-line signal, for a new cohort rate of 1.0 which is not below the baseline; no low-value source is added, since a baseline-only zone with no first-line signal and a media aggregator are both rejected; and a negative control proves the gate genuinely protects quality, since admitting the rejected candidates would drop the rate to 0.8, below the baseline. Each admitted zone carries a 2016 cursor; the deliverables include a marginal value report and per-zone health. Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
